{"tid":1141523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白金漢宮：梅根誕下兒子 丈夫哈利陪伴在側","createTime":"2019-05-06T13:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T15:41:43.000Z","uid":102732,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ecc707d7b7b1d1b1f486232d0fb4fbeccaf37c7a","tid":1141523,"uid":102732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:55:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%99%BD%E9%87%91%E6%BC%A2%E5%AE%AE%EF%BC%9A%E6%A2%85%E6%A0%B9%E8%AA%95%E4%B8%8B%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E3%80%80%E4%B8%88%E5%A4%AB%E5%93%88%E5%88%A9%E9%99%AA%E4%BC%B4%E5%9C%A8%E5%81%B4-134847433.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2599%25BD%25E9%2587%2591%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E5%25AE%25AE%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%25A2%2585%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E8%25AA%2595%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25AD%2590%25E3%2580%2580%25E4%25B8%2588%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E5%2593%2588%25E5%2588%25A9%25E9%2599%25AA%25E4%25BC%25B4%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%2581%25B4-134847433.html&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHiKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=e6f785b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%99%BD%E9%87%91%E6%BC%A2%E5%AE%AE%EF%BC%9A%E6%A2%85%E6%A0%B9%E8%AA%95%E4%B8%8B%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E3%80%80%E4%B8%88%E5%A4%AB%E5%93%88%E5%88%A9%E9%99%AA%E4%BC%B4%E5%9C%A8%E5%81%B4-134847433.html</a><br />\n<br />\n英國哈利王子和梅根在結婚一周年前夕，白金漢宮於周一（6日）宣布，37歲的梅根當日早上開始作動，已到產房分娩，丈夫哈利陪伴在側。哈利其後宣布，梅根平安誕下兒子，重7磅3安士。哈利及梅根的皇室寶寶將會是英女王伊利沙伯二世的第8個曾孫，亦在皇位繼承順序排名第7位。<br />\n<br />\n英國皇室去年10月宣布梅根懷孕，預產期為4月底至5月初，但一直未有她誕嬰消息，有指因為BB遲遲未出生，需要醫生催生。哈利夫婦沒有公布誕嬰地點，但已排除跟隨威廉王子夫人凱瑟琳，在倫敦的醫院分娩。2人又表示事前沒有刻意找出胎兒的性別，引來外界揣測。近日已有不少記者和關心皇室的國民在倫敦以西的溫莎巿紥營，希望第一時間分享喜悅。<br />\n<br />\n之前一名女童向梅根提議將寶寶的名字改為「埃米」（Amy），梅根表示喜歡該個名字。根據英國網上博彩公司，寶寶名字的大熱門為維多利亞（Victoria）、戴安娜（Diana）、阿瑟（Arthur）和詹姆斯（James）。"},{"pid":"f40511dee2614f6d93146f14c150d3b5aec3ea5c","tid":1141523,"uid":151057,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:56:45.000Z","msg":"黑人王子，巴閉了"},{"pid":"ec80419d4ced509c8050585eb4708171999a49b0","tid":1141523,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:57:58.000Z","msg":"Dark Prince"},{"pid":"290a4a46c29bac628d1aed73f900c9e76a91627c","tid":1141523,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:01:24.000Z","msg":"黑馬王子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白馬王子outdated <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd14586b5f7f57a58b8ba942e685bd5601fc011","tid":1141523,"uid":45373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T15:26:01.000Z","msg":"diana <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04410b7087db5f21526ee9a465af639a71761d2e","tid":1141523,"uid":180707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T15:28:18.000Z","msg":"如果係黑色既話會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77677f6741792ea2e8b7e12ea2829edc81155df1","tid":1141523,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T15:41:43.000Z","msg":"完全唔想理呢個力架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}